name: Jumping Jacks
information: This is a warm up cardio exercise that will increase your stamina and keep you lifted throughout your exercise

name: Abdominal Crunches
information: Crunches help you build muscle. This exercise strengthens your core, which includes lower back muscles & obliques

name: Russian Twist
information: This is an effective way to build your core and shoulders. It is popular for athletes. Makes strong shoulders

name: Mountain Climber
information: This is a good exercise for targeting your whole body and for building cardio endurance and strength.

name: Plank
information: This exercise works on the obliques, helps to build core strength, engages muscle in the upper back

name: Leg Raises
information: This helps to lose weight from the legs, lower abdomen. Tones and strengthens muscles and glutes.
